# PLAN.md ŌĆö EVA Accelerator (46-accelerator)

**Project**: 46-accelerator ŌĆö EVA Domain Assistant Booking Portal
**Phase 1**: Fluent UI Migration ŌĆö COMPLETE 2026-02-23
