## Feature: Fluent UI Migration [ID=F46-01]

Replace legacy shadcn/radix scaffold with Fluent UI React v9 across all active screens.

### Story: Migrate App shell and navigation [ID=F46-01-001]

Remove external toaster. Wire `FluentProvider + webLightTheme`. Replace nav buttons with Fluent `Button`.
Accept: `npm run build` exits 0, no legacy UI imports in `App.tsx`.

### Story: Migrate BookingDialog to Fluent UI [ID=F46-01-002]

Migrate 3-step wizard: dialog, progress indicator, inputs, checkboxes, and actions.
Accept: All Fluent primitives; no radix/shadcn imports.

### Story: Migrate ExitSurveyDialog to Fluent UI [ID=F46-01-003]

Migrate dialog, fields, radio groups, and layout.

### Story: Migrate TeamManagementDialog to Fluent UI [ID=F46-01-004]

Migrate member form, role select, list row rendering, and badges.

### Story: Migrate MyBookings to Fluent UI [ID=F46-01-005]

Migrate cards, status badges, empty-state, and action buttons.

### Story: Migrate AdminDashboard to Fluent UI [ID=F46-01-006]

Migrate stat cards, utilization progress bars, and bookings table.

### Story: Wire localStorage persistence hook [ID=F46-01-007]

Implement `src/hooks/use-local-storage-state.ts` shared hook.
Replace all in-component state with localStorage-backed state for: bookings, entry-surveys, exit-surveys, team-members.

