## Feature: EVA Spark Design System Integration [ID=F46-02]

Replace raw `FluentProvider + webLightTheme` with the EVA Spark design system
from `@eva/gc-design-system` and `@eva/ui` (sourced from `../31-eva-faces/shared/`).

### Story: Wire @eva/gc-design-system and @eva/ui dependencies [ID=F46-02-001]

Add `file:../31-eva-faces/shared/gc-design-system` and `file:../31-eva-faces/shared/eva-ui` to package.json.
Add Vite aliases for `@eva/*` pointing to `../31-eva-faces/shared/*/src`.
Add tsconfig.json path mappings.
Accept: `npm run build` exits 0 with both packages resolved.

### Story: Replace FluentProvider with GCThemeProvider in App.tsx [ID=F46-02-002]

Remove `import { FluentProvider, webLightTheme }`. Wrap app in `<GCThemeProvider variant="light">`.
Accept: App renders; Fluent tokens still resolve via GCThemeProvider.

### Story: Replace raw Button with EvaButton in App.tsx navigation [ID=F46-02-003]

All 8 navigation tab buttons use `EvaButton` from `@eva/ui`.
Accept: Nav renders; `variant` prop used instead of `appearance`.

